    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, ideally for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine is currently running roughly and requires significant mechanical attention, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. The exterior has several large dents and peeling clear coat, and the interior shows heavy wear and tear, including some tears in the upholstery. It will likely need to be towed and will require a comprehensive overhaul to be roadworthy again.",
      "price": 4500.0,
